WEBVTT

00:03.456 --> 00:06.576
The name of the ship
on which Sinbad sailed!

00:06.656 --> 00:08.976
Lord Akbari, please, I beg you!

00:09.056 --> 00:11.776
I'm only a humble Harbour Master.

00:11.856 --> 00:13.696
I don't know!

00:13.776 --> 00:15.496
Then what use are you to me?

00:16.976 --> 00:19.016
No!

00:20.816 --> 00:22.296
Master.

00:30.296 --> 00:32.695
There's only one way
to find Sinbad now.

